nt-size:17px\"><em>Nature</em>, in the common sense, refers to essences unchanged by man; space, the air, the river, the leaf.&nbsp;<em>Art</em>&nbsp;is applied to the mixture of his will with the same things, as in a house, a canal, a statue, a picture. </p>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"has-text-color\" style=\"color:#000000;font-size:17px\">But his operations taken together are so insignificant, a little chipping, baking, patching, and washing, that in an impression so grand as that of the world on the human mind, they do not vary the result.</p>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33%\">\n<div style=\"height:2vw\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"></div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.8/outside-01.jpg\" alt=\"Il sole che tramonta attraverso una fitta foresta di alberi.\" /></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33.62%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.8/outside-02.jpg\" alt=\"Turbine eoliche in piedi su una pianura erbosa, con un cielo blu sullo sfondo.\" /></figure>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-columns alignwide is-layout-flex wp-container-181 wp-block-columns-is-layout-flex\">\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:69%\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://s.w.org/images/core/5.8/outside-03.jpg\" alt=\"Il sole splende su un crinale che conduce alla costa. In lontananza, un\'auto scende lungo una strada.\" /></figure>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-column is-vertically-aligned-center is-layout-flow wp-block-column-is-layout-flow\" style=\"flex-basis:33%\">\n<div style=\"height:2vw\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\">